    fix: strip IDE binaries from deploy zip (~600MB → ~30MB)
    
    @github/copilot has ripgrep, tree-sitter, voice engine, prebuilt
    binaries for IDE use only. Strip them before zipping for Azure.
    Also remove @esbuild and typescript (devDependencies not needed).
    
    Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>

diff --git a/.github/workflows/deploy-backend.yml b/.github/workflows/deploy-backend.yml
